{"id": 243327964, "title": "Exclusive: Anant-Radhika&#039;s sangeet ceremony likely to portray their love story", "text": "Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant's wedding is the talk of the town and the preparations for their sangeet ceremony have already begun. As their grand pre-wedding festivities are underway, sources told India Today TV that the sangeet ceremony would witness dance performances by friends of the bride and the groom. Sources also said the two sides would portray Anant and Radhika's love story, capturing how they met and planned on spending the rest of their lives with each other. To add up, the songs would be a mix of Western and Bollywood, comprising Radhika's favourites (Katy Perry, Britney Spears, Rihanna, and more).The ceremony is also likely to include performances from Bollywood stars invited to attend the pre-wedding festivity. Anant Ambani and Radhika Merchant will get married in a grand ceremony in Mumbai on July 12.The celebrations will continue on Saturday, July 13, with 'Shubh Aashirwad'.The final event, 'Mangal Utsav' or the wedding reception, is scheduled for Sunday, July 14.Published By: Vani MehrotraPublished On: Jun 29, 2024Must Watch", "summary": "<a href=\"https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/anant-ambani-radhika-merchant-pre-wedding-festivities-sangeet-ceremony-ambani-wedding-2559980-2024-06-29\"> <img align=\"left\" hspace=\"2\" height=\"180\" width=\"305\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/anant-ambaniradhika-merchant-295943738-16x9_0.jpg?VersionId=txZ4K8dBVzmtdEKGgElC2yynwiZg.Fbk\"> </a> Exclusive: Anant-Radhika's sangeet ceremony likely to portray their love story", "url": "https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/anant-ambani-radhika-merchant-pre-wedding-festivities-sangeet-ceremony-ambani-wedding-2559980-2024-06-29", "image": "https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202406/anant-ambaniradhika-merchant-295943738-16x9_0.jpg?VersionId=txZ4K8dBVzmtdEKGgElC